{"body": "I know it's a pain, but you can downgrade to 4.0.0-beta1 and run your migrations every time you need to add an array column. Or you can put <code>gem 'rails', github: 'scudco/rails', branch: '10432-fix-add-column-with-array'</code> in your Gemfile for now, though it is rebased on top of some other changes you may or may not want.\r\n\r\nYou can also just write the SQL yourself and have custom <code>up</code> and <code>down</code> methods in your migrations.\r\n\r\n@muichkine changing your schema won't have any effect unless you are doing a <code>rake db:schema:load</code>.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/17609571", "created_at": "2013-05-08T14:31:05Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10482#issuecomment-17609571", "updated_at": "2013-05-08T14:31:05Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10482, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/scudco", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/7bdb696ac0f589522c9ed31a1b24057b?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F5e7264477cf9b6b237a0d254cf0324e2.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/received_events", "gravatar_id": "7bdb696ac0f589522c9ed31a1b24057b", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "scudco", "type": "User", "id": 3806, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scudco/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237de52bd3543c151008be3"}, "id": 17609571, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10482"}
